{"type":null,"faqId":37085,"title":"如何设置使用运动轨迹功能？哪些系统支持此功能？","answer":"<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">\n<div style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\" id=\"softwareDescription\" jQuery17105968387367496105=\"16\">\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">目前，安卓系统和IOS系统的APP均已支持此功能。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">运动轨迹的展示是依靠手机和华为APP共同合作的，这也是业界的惯用方式。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">运动轨迹操作方式：</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">1、确保手机出于联网状态并打开GPS功能；</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">2、打开华为运动穿戴APP，进入右侧菜单；</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">3、进入“运动轨迹”菜单，点击开始即可；（备注：android系统可在点击开始前设置运动目标）</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">4、运动结束后可以，还以分享运动数据。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">注：此功能需要手机GPS配合使用，可以记录单次运动消耗的卡路里，运动距离，速度及步数等信息；</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\">地图由高德地图提供，由于受高德地图覆盖区域限制，现仅支持中国大陆及香港、澳门等地。</p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 2em; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px\"><a href=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/805e0_c2fke.png\" jQuery17105968387367496105=\"22\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://app.huawei.com/tkb/ha-i/805e0_c2fke.png\"></a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","faqTypeId":203,"faqType":"兼容与支持","useful":6,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2249","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-System-Requirements-Support","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750142000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":295,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,运动轨迹,GPS","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}